nd compassionate environment where we support each other and enable employees to spend valuable time with their families during times of need our time off policies give all employees the ability to take the time away from work to be there for their families at these critical moments we offer compassionate leave up to five days per year bereavement leave up to  days amount varies based on situation and up to twelve weeks of paid parental leave us only and generous leave policies in our international locations comprehensive health  compensation plans we provide a variety of programs to support your health and financial security some of these programs include great health insurance including a fsa or hsa which includes a company contribution dental  vision coverage k match program employee assistance program life and disability equity  employee stock purchase plan espp and generous pto and holiday schedule employee  family fun we love to take advantage of holidays and the opportunity to get together and enjoy some down time summer picnics halloween competitions we are very serious about halloween cultural celebrations and holiday craft events for the vocera kids are some of the events we look forward to all year events will vary around the globe but everyone has fun employee referral bonuses finding the right blend of talent and cultural fit to add to our teams is invaluable our employee referral program rewards employees who actively seek other talented people to join the vocera team we offer a generous referral bonus for successfully referring new employees employee discount program our passport unlimited corporate discount program provides our employees access to a wide range of products goods and services at a discounted rate there is but one goal to make your life easier by saving you time and money youll find special offers on services retail stores restaurants entertainment  travel and much more volunteer time off giving back to our communities is important to us our volunteer time off program is designed to provide employees with paid time to participate in voceras community involvement and charity events that give back to our local communities employee community involvement council ecic our ecic is an employeerun community involvement team that works to promote employee unity and a sense of community in and out of the office the ecic was chartered to encourage employees to be positive forces in their communities around the globe the mission of the ecic is to give back to the communities that vocera serves through financial support and the energy and passion of all its employees who are located around the globe employee recognition bravo as a way to recognize each other vocera encourages all employees to celebrate others through our recognition and reward program the program provides the opportunity to acknowledge others who drive for results demonstrate and uphold our company values and go above and beyond every day this social network communication platform shines a light on how important and impressive every employee across the company is to vocera’s collective success through appreciation recognition and rewards the bravo program allows all employees to reinforce the positive energy at vocera oh and you get to buy cool stuff with your reward points good eats who doesnt like good food and snacks depending on your location there are lots of choices for you catered lunches subsidized vending machines fresh fruit food truck tuesdays and monthly bagel socials miscellaneous we also offer a variety of other programs and services depending on location and country onsite dry cleaning delivery service amusement park discounts california golf discounts cellular service discounts and more come join us nbsp     vocera values think customer first customers are top of mind in all the decisions we make as a company we try to walk in the shoes of our customers we listen and connect with customers and coworkers lead with passion we are committed to the success of the organization we have a shared passion for our mission of improving lives by delivering breakthrough communications experiences embrace innovation we seek out and embrace innovation and use it to our competitive advantage by being agile and innovative we can successfully respond to change and drive continuous improvement as we grow drive for results we are focused on achieving the company results and minimizing interference and distractions that can detract from achieving those results we value results more than activity build with respect we strive to build people processes and a great company while we treat others the way we would want to be treated namely with integrity and respect   find your place at vocera the vocera brand and solutions are represented by a specific universal archetype translator or “messenger of meaning” vocera provides integrated intelligent communication to instantly connect people in insightful empathetic and delightful ways stay connected           about us experience innovation network leadership board members investors careers customer stories partners vocera in the global community locations contact us news  events press releases news and research events social media newsfeed resource center case studies data sheets documentation  guides solution briefs videos webinars white papers  race street san jose ca  united states vocera get started who we are vocera empowers people in missioncritical environments to instantly connect via secure mobile integrated and intelligent communication solutions the vocera vision   how to buy contact vocera contact a sales specialist about vocera solutions   contact sales   phone vocera     contact us tech support  supportvoceracom partners partnersvoceracom sales vocera saleswebvoceracom   customer partner and support portal access  vocera skip to main content questions vocera blog   support portal questions vocera contact us you are herehome » services  support vocera por