mmunication solutions for mobile workers in healthcare hospitality energy education and other industries the companys segments include product and service the companys solutions include the vocera communication system vocera care experience vocera engage integration platform smartphone applications and its experience innovation networkthe companys vocera communication system consists of a software platform that connects communication devices including its handsfree wearable voicecontrolled communication badges and thirdparty mobile devices that use its software applications to become part of the vocera system the system transforms the way mobile workers communicate by enabling them to instantly connect through voice or text messaging with the right person simply by saying or selecting the name function or group name of the person they want to reach often while remaining at the pointofcare the companys vocera communication platform contains an optimized speech recognition engine call routing and management functionality reporting and analytics tools clinical directories and user profiles its communication badge is a wearable device weighing less than over two ounces that operates over customers industrystandard wireless fidelity wifi networks its communication badge incorporates automatic diagnostic mechanisms that feed data on wireless network performance back to the software platform for reporting and diagnosis of problemsthe companys vocera collaboration suite provides a multimode communications and collaboration experience combining the calling texting alerting and content distribution capabilities of vocera into a smartphone application its vocera secure texting is an alternative to nonsecure short message service sms texting that enables health insurance portability and accountability hipaacompliance and includes its cloudbased secure texting application extending the power of the vocera communication platform to physicians and care teams that are located both inside and outside the hospital the companys vocera care experience is a hosted software suite which offers caregivers communication solutions that span the entire care continuum before admission during treatment and after discharge vocera care experience modules include prearrival communication good to go care calls and care roundsthe companys professional services help customers deploy manage update andor expand their vocera systems the company offers a range of services including clinical workflow design wireless assessment solution configuration training and project management enabling customers to integrate its solutions the company also provides classroom and distance learning curricula for systems administrators information technology it professionals and clinical educators the company provides round the clock technical support to its customers through its support centers in san jose california fort wayne indiana toronto canada knoxville tennessee and reading united kingdom additional services including an annual remote system health assessment and biweekly technical webinar education are offered as projectbased consulting or through its membership collaborative the experience innovation network is a membership program that collaborates with healthcare provider organizations to further the development of innovations and solutions the company provides classroom training distance learning or customized courseware covering best practices implementation and use of its solutions training courses are provided for systems administrators it professionals and industryspecific end user educatorsthe company competes with cisco systems ascom and spectralink » full overview of vcran company address vocera communications inc  race st ste san jose   ca    p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation robert zollars  brent lang  justin spencer  paul johnson  jay spitzen  » more officers  directors vocera communications inc news briefvocera reports q 